      "title": "Monkeypox cases exceed 50,000 - WHO",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Statistics show that more than 50,000 monkeypox cases have been reported to the World Health Organization in this year's global epidemic.",
        "Data from the United Nations Health Agency or World Health Organization, which declared the outbreak a global public health emergency in July, showed that 50,496 cases and 16 deaths have been reported so far."
